belongs_to_collection.name: Treasure Island Media's L.U.S.T. (Lost Unreleased Sex Tapes) Collection

original_title: L.U.S.T. (Lost Unreleased Sex Tapes) 3: "What I Can't See" Edition
overview: Deep in the Treasure Island Media video vault were found several hard drives that had a ton of unreleased footage on them. You won't believe what was unearthed and never released — until now – newly edited and remastered! Lost Unreleased Sex Tapes is a lost moment in sexual time and Treasure Island Media history. Each scene is a gem. Many of these guys stopped doing porn, some moved away, and some we still work with today. Volume 3 features many All-Star Hall-Of-Fame exclusives (including Derek Anthony, Dan Fisk, Ian Jay, Brad McGuire, James Roscoe, Jerry Stearns, and Will), some favorites over the years (including Jaison Lawrence, Damon Darko, Fred Mayer, Jake Fillups, Tommy Haine, and Ross X), and many, many more.
title: L.U.S.T. (Lost Unreleased Sex Tapes) 3: "What I Can't See" Edition
